aa(lp83
VSo what do we do about it?
p84
aVWell, preventing infection
p85
aVis either about protecting people or about eliminating the mosquitoes.
p86
aVLet's focus on people first.
p87
aVYou can get vaccinated.
p88
aVYou can not travel to Zika areas.
p89
aVOr you can cover up and apply insect repellent.
p90
aVGetting vaccinated is not an option, because there isn't a vaccine yet
p91
aVand there probably won't be for a couple of years.
p92
aVStaying home isn't a foolproof protection either
p93
aVbecause we now know that it can be sexually transmitted.
p94
aVCovering up and applying insect repellent does work ...
p95
aa(lp96
Vuntil you forget.
